Package org.hypermedea.pddl.planners

Class NativePlannerWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hypermedea.pddl.planners.PlannerWrapper
      • org.hypermedea.pddl.planners.NativePlannerWrapper
  • public class NativePlannerWrapper
extends PlannerWrapper
    Wrapper for a PDDL planner provided as a native program (called in a subprocess). The program's output is parsed according to the rules given in VAL. A plan is a sequence of steps 0: STEP1\n 1: STEP2\n... where each step is one of:
    • NAME ARG1 ARG2 .. ARGN
    • (NAME ARG1 ARG2 .. ARGN) (TODO)
    • NAME [ARG1 ARG2 .. ARGN] (TODO)
